OL,3,CA decade since Storm Abigail: Why does
OL,4,Cthe Met Office name storms?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Weather Producer
OL,7,FJennifer Mawby
OL,9,FTen years ago today the first storm
OL,10,Fwas named by the Met Office.
OL,12,FStorm Abigail hit northwest Scotland
OL,13,Fon 10 November 2015, bringing strong
OL,14,Fwinds and heavy rainfall and leaving
OL,15,F20,000 homes without power.
OL,17,FSince then 70 storms have been named,
OL,18,Flisted each year in alphabetical order.
OL,20,FSo why did we start naming storms?
