OL,3,CA decade since Storm Abigail: Why does
OL,4,Cthe Met Office name storms?
OL,6,FThe Storms Western Europe naming
OL,7,Fgroup, made up of the Met Office in
OL,8,Fthe UK, Met Eireann in Ireland and
OL,9,FKNMI in the Netherlands collaborate to
OL,10,Fmake an alphabetical list of names
OL,11,Fbased on suggestions from the public.
OL,13,FStorm season begins at the start of
OL,14,FSeptember and runs through to the end
OL,15,Fof August the following year, to
OL,16,Fcoincide with when low pressure
OL,17,Fweather systems are more likely to
OL,18,Fdominate our climate.
