OL,3,CA decade since Storm Abigail: Why does
OL,4,Cthe Met Office name storms?
OL,6,FAt the start of October the UK battled
OL,7,FStorm Amy, and the next to hit will be
OL,8,Fcalled Bram.
OL,10,FHowever, the last storm parts of the
OL,11,FUK experienced was called Storm
OL,12,FBenjamin because it was named by
OL,13,FFrance's weather service Meteo France
OL,14,Ffirst.
OL,16,FWho can suggest a name?
OL,18,FAnyone who fancies having a storm
OL,19,Fnamed after them can email their
OL,20,Fsuggestions to the Met Office via
OL,21,Ftheir website.
